      "span_text": "More details about the PD is described here, so that what we considered something comparable with 'curriculum innovation' [CITATION_1] , in our case PD with embedded curriculum supports, is clearly articulated, especially since we are investigating the potential it has for causing (un)predicted changes in science teacher orientations."
